❯ scoop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Usage: scoop &amp;lt;command&amp;gt; [&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Some useful commands are:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;alias       Manage scoop aliases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;bucket      Manage Scoop buckets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;cache       Show or &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;clear&lt;/span&gt; the download cache&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;checkup     Check &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; potential problems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;cleanup     Cleanup apps &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;by&lt;/span&gt; removing old versions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;config      Get or &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;set&lt;/span&gt; configuration values&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;create      Create a custom &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt; manifest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;depends     &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;List&lt;/span&gt; dependencies &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;an&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;export      Exports (&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;an&lt;/span&gt; importable) &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt; of installed apps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt;        Show &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for